note_en:'Roll out the strudel pastry paper-thin with oil. Arrange sliced apples with breadcrumbs, raisins, pine nuts, cinnamon and sugar. Roll up carefully using a cloth. Brush with melted butter and bake at 190Â°C for 35 minutes.',
